 database? our primary mode of retrieving this information?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Ocular Character Recognition tries to put the focus of digitization back
 on the human experience, and preserving human culture by reversing the
 process of digitization, defamiliarizing the familiar, and reclaiming the
 physical/claiming the digital.
